A rape case is being heard. The accused is an 85-year-old old man. The judge says:
- The defendant, on May 15 of this year at 20 o'clock you raped a student Ivanova in Medvedkovo, at 21 o'clock in Izmailovsky Park you raped a saleswoman Petrova, then at 22 o'clock at Yaroslavsky railway station you raped a student of vocational school Sidorova. Explain to the court how you did it, how is it even possible at your age?
- And why is it not possible? I have a motorcycle!
